verbose_text: The differentiation process is MYB independent and associated with HOXA expression (Buchrieser, James, & Moore, 2017; Dou et al., 2016; Ivanovs et al., 2017; Ng et al., 2016; Vanhee et al., 2015), indicating this recapitulates primitive hematopoiesis in vivo.
evidence: MYB-independent and associated with HOXA expression
